<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/* MVP float parsing trick: send x/y/z/radius scaled by 1000 as integers
