<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]">Introducing small-step operational semantics for the core event types would provide an unambiguous, mathematical description of state evolution, strengthening claims of determinism and facilitating formal verification or proof-assisted extensions.</li>
