<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]">It serves as foundational infrastructure for subsequent refinements (e.g., entropy-based scheduling or capability models) by establishing a formal baseline for kernel behavior.</li>
</ul>
